{
  "stem": "16163.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how she met him, I believe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was the one who started a [?youth?] school over there and put young children together into the houses surrounded by the church, those two buildings.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told my mother that I should not be in the house with [? her. ?] I would be much better off if I would be with the younger children together.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's how I got into that home there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We called it a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And unfortunately, I took very sick right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was put in what we called a children's [GERMAN], meaning a children's-- like a hospice, hospital type of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Which I stayed from September '42 till April '43.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very long time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had rheumatic fever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't move around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was practically paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was very fortunate in one way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had the Jewish doctors from [INAUDIBLE] and Prague and they really saved my life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's another story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had medications, which people had on them when they got to Theresienstadt, and it was taken away from everybody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from that, they made like a [NON-ENGLISH] center, like a drug center.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had a Jewish man who was leading this whole thing and gave out the medication when it was needed, all right?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It turned out if he could have been alive after the war, he would have been my father-in-law.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother had to go from where she worked to this particular place to get the medication.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She worked, in matter of fact, for people with TB, because she had the experience through my father, and there was like a little hospital.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not a hospital-- but, you know, like a-- a room area where they only had TB patients.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
